{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-blog-tsx","path":"/zh/blog/","result":{"data":{"locales":{"edges":[{"node":{"ns":"index","data":"{\"about\":\"關於我\",\"comments\":\"評論\",\"home\":\"家\",\"blog\":\"文章\",\"project\":\"作品\",\"contact\":\"聯絡我\",\"contact-form-title\":\"歡迎留下任何你想說的話 🙏\",\"contact-form-name\":\"你的名稱\",\"contact-form-messages\":\"想說的話\",\"submit\":\"送出\",\"close\":\"關閉\",\"contact-form-success\":\"🎉 已成功送出 🎉\",\"contact-form-errors\":\"抱歉😿\\n好像有什麼出錯了\",\"found-nothing\":\"沒有找到文章...\",\"themeTitle\":\"主題模式\",\"dark\":\"深色\",\"light\":\"淺色\",\"languageTitle\":\"選擇語言\",\"zh\":\"中文\",\"en\":\"英文\",\"workInProgress\":\"努力產出中...\",\"image-source\":\"圖片來源 unsplash\"}","language":"zh"}}]},"articles":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"name":"from-js-to-ts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"從Js寫到Ts","date":"2022-10-17T10:50:55.802Z","image_cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621839673705-6617adf9e890?fit=crop&w=1000&q=80","type":"blog"},"html":"<h1>從 Javascript 到 typescript</h1>\n<p>原本的部落格專案是用 js 開發的<br>\n後來覺得 是時候加入一點新的東西了<br>\n其實之前也寫過一點點 ts 了<br>\n不過之前是最一開始就決定試著寫 ts<br>\n這次則是從原本的 js 轉過去</p>\n<p>總之就開始吧～<br>\n首先...\n把專案名稱是 .js 的檔案改成 .ts\n.jsx 改成 .tsx<br>\n以及把 jsconfig.json 改成 tsconfig.json\n就完成啦 🎉\n因為 Gatsby 原生就支援了這兩種寫法<br>\n所以其實很方便～</p>\n<p>接著要改的東西有<br>\n<code>gastby-config.js -> gastby-config.ts</code>;</p>\n<details>\n<summary>gastby-config.ts</summary>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { GatsbyConfig } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;gatsby&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">*</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">as</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> dotenv </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;dotenv&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  dotenv.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">config</span><span class=\"mtk1\">({ path: __dirname </span><span class=\"mtk7\">+</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;/.env&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> });</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">default</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    siteMetadata: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    title: </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// name your site,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    siteUrl: </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// your site&#39;s url,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    },</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    plugins: [</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk7\">...</span><span class=\"mtk1\">all plugins you needed</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    ],</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">as</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5 mtku\">GatsbyConfig</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n</details>\n</br>\n<p><code>gastby-node.js -> gastby-node.ts</code>;</p>\n<details>\n<summary>gastby-node.ts</summary>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { GatsbyNode } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;gatsby&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">*</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">as</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> path </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;path&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">onCreateWebpackConfig</span><span class=\"mtk7\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5 mtku\">GatsbyNode</span><span class=\"mtk1\">[</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;onCreateWebpackConfig&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">] </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> ({</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  actions,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}) </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  actions.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">setWebpackConfig</span><span class=\"mtk1\">({</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    resolve: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      alias: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@components&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: path.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">resolve</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(__dirname, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;src/components&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">),</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@pages&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: path.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">resolve</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(__dirname, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;src/pages&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">),</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@layouts&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: path.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">resolve</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(__dirname, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;src/layouts&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">),</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@mock&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: path.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">resolve</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(__dirname, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;src/mock&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">),</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@images&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: path.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">resolve</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(__dirname, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;src/images&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">),</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@tool&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: path.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">resolve</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(__dirname, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;src/tool&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">),</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@static&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: path.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">resolve</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(__dirname, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;static&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">),</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      },</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    },</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  });</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>這個設定是讓我可以使用類似縮寫功能的\n因為在專案裡有時候會要載入別的元件\n這時候會寫 import \"../../components/some-components\"\n這個縮寫讓他可以是 import \"@components/some-components\"\n讓版面不會太亂</p>\n</blockquote>\n</details>\n</br>\n<p><code>gastby-browser.jsx -> gastby-browser.tsx</code>;</p>\n<details>\n<summary>gastby-browser.tsx</summary>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">*</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">as</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> React </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;react&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> type { GatsbyBrowser } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;gatsby&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> Layout </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@components/layout&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 你可以加入自己設計的Layout Container</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">wrapPageElement</span><span class=\"mtk7\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5 mtku\">GatsbyBrowser</span><span class=\"mtk1\">[</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;wrapPageElement&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">] </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> ({</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  element,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}) </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">return</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">Layout</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Hello World&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">h1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      {element}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">Layout</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  );</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>這個目前先這樣就行了 這樣就讓 Layout 會在每一頁裡面呈現 不需要分別加進去<br>\n不過之後因為我在處理 i18n 的時候 遇到了一點問題 會改動到這裡的設置\n先這樣 👋</p>\n</blockquote>\n</details>\n</br>\n<p>接著就可以進行元件裡的調整了<br>\n雖然 typescript 融入 react 貌似有很多種寫法（泛型之類的）<br>\n但因為我還沒有到很熟悉<br>\n所以暫時先改成一個元件配上 propTypes 的方式<br>\n以後更理解泛型的寫法 會再來補上來的 ～～～</p>\n<p>我大部分遇到的 type 寫法 多半直接參考官網的<br>\n我覺得官網的 handbook 寫的很好<br>\n關於 typescript 我會繼續努力學習的<br>\n之後應該也會慢慢的分享這些部分</p>\n<p>以上是今天的分享 👋</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .abyss { background-color: #000c18; }\n  .abyss .mtki { font-style: italic; }\n  .abyss .mtku {\n    text-decoration: underline;\n    text-underline-position: under;\n  }\n  .abyss .mtk1 { color: #6688CC; }\n  .abyss .mtk7 { color: #225588; }\n  .abyss .mtk11 { color: #22AA44; }\n  .abyss .mtk4 { color: #F280D0; }\n  .abyss .mtk6 { color: #DDBB88; }\n  .abyss .mtk3 { color: #384887; }\n  .abyss .mtk5 { color: #FFEEBB; }\n  .abyss .mtk15 { color: #9966B8; }\n  .abyss .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n</style>"}},{"node":{"fields":{"name":"build-gastby-blog"},"frontmatter":{"title":"今天來建立Gatsby部落格","date":"2022-10-11T09:55:11.312Z","image_cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542903660-eedba2cda473?fit=crop&w=1000&q=80","type":"blog"},"html":"<h1>架起你的部落格</h1>\n<p>我是採用 Gatsby 的 Quick start<br>\n首先要確定自己的 node 版本有在 14.15 以上<br>\n不然啟動伺服器的時候會遇到打不開的問題</p>\n<p>使用命令提示字元(cmd) 來建立這次的專案\n用指令快速建起一個 Gatsby 專案<br>\n<code>npm init gatsby</code><br>\n輸入完後 照著題目選擇你想要的語言/插件/額外功能：</p>\n<p>我的設定檔如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">What would you like to call your site</span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 取名字</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">✔ · My Gatsby Site</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">What would you like to name the folder where your site will be created</span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 取資料夾名稱</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">✔ </span><span class=\"mtk7\">/</span><span class=\"mtk1\">my</span><span class=\"mtk7\">-</span><span class=\"mtk1\">gatsby</span><span class=\"mtk7\">-</span><span class=\"mtk1\">site</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">✔ Will you be using JavaScript or TypeScript</span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 選擇 js || ts</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">· JavaScript</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">✔ Will you be using a CMS</span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 需不需要額外的內容管理系統</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">· </span><span class=\"mtk6\">No</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (or I</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;ll add it later</span><span class=\"mtk8\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">✔ Would you like to install a styling system</span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 需要用什麼樣式套件</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">· styled</span><span class=\"mtk7\">-</span><span class=\"mtk1\">domponents</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> Would you like to install additional features with other plugins</span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 多選 可以選GA, sitemap, md/mdx</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">(Multiple choice) Use arrow keys to move, spacebar to select, and confirm with an enter on </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;Done&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">❯◯ Add the Google Analytics tracking script</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ Add responsive images</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◉ Add an automatic sitemap</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ Generate a manifest file</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◉ Add Markdown and MDX support</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ Add Markdown </span><span class=\"mtk6\">support</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (without MDX)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>我選了 js (後面會提我把 js 轉成 ts 的過程)<br>\n樣式選擇 styled-components<br>\n沒有使用 CMS 而是直接用 md 檔， 所以加裝了 md/mdx support</p>\n<p>完成後 你的網站就可以跑起來了 ～<br>\n在 cmd 中 把本地端伺服器架起來<br>\n<code>npm run develop</code><br>\n然後開啟瀏覽器 輸入網址： <a href=\"http://localhost:8000\">http://localhost:8000</a><br>\n就可以看到你的網站了 🎉<br>\n之後就可以藉由編輯 src/pages/index.js 這個檔案<br>\n然後就可以馬上在畫面上看到更新<br>\n接著我會分享一些功能</p>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> js to ts</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> theme 暗黑模式</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> i18n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> deploy to github-page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以上是今天的分享 👋</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .abyss { background-color: #000c18; }\n  .abyss .mtk1 { color: #6688CC; }\n  .abyss .mtk7 { color: #225588; }\n  .abyss .mtk3 { color: #384887; }\n  .abyss .mtk6 { color: #DDBB88; }\n  .abyss .mtk11 { color: #22AA44; }\n  .abyss .mtk8 { color: #F8F8F0; }\n  .abyss .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n</style>"}},{"node":{"fields":{"name":"gatsby-blog"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby用起來_架起專案","date":"2022-09-13T04:42:09.509Z","image_cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615419235091-59bf9cbd530b?fit=crop&w=1000&q=100","type":"blog"},"html":"<h1>開始用 Gatsby 來架我的部落格</h1>\n<p>之前試著用 hexo 來架部落格<br>\n可以在短時間裡就把一個網站架好<br>\n真的是很快</p>\n<p>主題也有滿多可以在官網裡找<br>\n或者別人寫好的主題可以直接套來用<br>\n不過 有時候就是<br>\n覺得有些主題裡總是差了一點功能\n但自己要調整的話 也是滿費勁的</p>\n<p>後來發現 Gatsby<br>\n覺得這套更有彈性<br>\n對我來說比較容易新增自己想要的功能<br>\n雖然彈性就代表著自己會花更多心力<br>\n不過我很享受 創造的過程</p>\n<p>雖然也有其他別的 React 相關框架可以當成部落格的<br>\n我想 next.js 或 remix.js<br>\n都可以很快地架出部落格 也有很多強大的功能<br>\n不過 覺得自己的部落格其實只需要靜態的呈現就足矣<br>\n所以就決定要使用 Gatsby 了！！</p>\n<p>之後會慢慢補一些在建立專案的時候 遇到的一些困難 😂<br>\n以上是今天的分享 👋</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n</style>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"language":"zh","i18n":{"language":"zh","languages":["en","zh"],"defaultLanguage":"en","generateDefaultLanguagePage":false,"routed":true,"originalPath":"/blog/","path":"zh/blog/"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3764592887"]}